Right.

00:56:23.040 --> 00:56:24.040
And

00:56:24.040 --> 00:56:26.040
if you only do values,

00:56:26.040 --> 00:56:28.040
it will depend on

00:56:28.040 --> 00:56:30.040
which one it will take first.

00:56:30.040 --> 00:56:32.040
Sometimes I will want to say,

00:56:32.040 --> 00:56:33.040
okay,

00:56:33.040 --> 00:56:34.040
classic to green,

00:56:34.040 --> 00:56:35.040
like a net.

00:56:35.040 --> 00:56:36.040
Some other

00:56:36.040 --> 00:56:38.040
plotting libraries

00:56:38.040 --> 00:56:39.040
you have the fact that

